    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.cos(((v2 + 0.96 / tmp + 0.88) - (v2 + 0.27 - v2 + 0.61)))
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.exp(v2 + 0.30) / wp.abs(tmp + 0.21)))
    tmp = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.12 / v2 + 0.74)) / (wp.exp(tmp + 0.46) - (v1 + 0.35 - v2 + 0.51)))
    tmp = (v2 * wp.cos(v2))
    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.62 + v2 + 0.75)) * ((tmp + 0.13 * v0 + 0.85) * wp.exp(v2 + 0.64)))
    data[tid] = v0
